Sentencas: Thermoelectric power and electrical conductivity of pure and 5, 10 and 20% strontium-doped lanthanum manganite are determined as function of temperature in air and of P-O2 at 1000 degrees C.
Titulo: Thermoelectric power and electrical conductivity of strontium-doped lanthanum manganite

Sentencas: At high temperatures the thermoelectric power is negative.
Titulo: Thermoelectric power and electrical conductivity of strontium-doped lanthanum manganite

Sentencas: Both thermoelectric power and conductivity are found to be nearly independent of doping at high temperatures, but not at low.
Titulo: Thermoelectric power and electrical conductivity of strontium-doped lanthanum manganite

Sentencas: This can be explained if it is assumed that Mn3+ disproportionates into Mn2+ and Mn4+.
Titulo: Thermoelectric power and electrical conductivity of strontium-doped lanthanum manganite

Sentencas: In reducing atmospheres the thermoelectric power is found to be only slightly dependent on P-O2, which also might be explained by the disproportionation reaction.
Titulo: Thermoelectric power and electrical conductivity of strontium-doped lanthanum manganite
